      • mapDecorationTableContent

        public static void mapDecorationTableContent​(DecorationTablePOJO pojo,
                                             DecorationTableParsingResult res,
                                             DecorationTable decorationTable)
        Main mapper enabling DecorationTablePOJO transformation to DecorationTable. If an error occurs, then the result will not contain any decoration table value. Error are added to DecorationTableParsingResult object.
        Parameters:
        pojo - The mapped DecorationTablePOJO related to the Seed Transducer JSON file
        res - The DecorationTableParsingResult parsing result (modified by process)
        decorationTable - The DecorationTable parsed object (modified by process)

      • mapToVariable

        private static Variable mapToVariable​(java.lang.String tabColumn,
                                      int tabLine,
                                      java.lang.String semanticLetter,
                                      java.lang.String pojoName,
                                      java.util.Optional<java.lang.String> pojoIndex,
                                      DecorationTableParsingResult res)
        Maps given pojo value to model Variable. Errors are added to DecorationTableParsingResult.
        Parameters:
        tabColumn - The concerned column in the decoration table (Register, Return, Update or Guard).
        tabLine - The table line corresponding to this instruction
        semanticLetter - The semantic letter corresponding to this instruction
        pojoName - The pojo name to map from
        pojoIndex - The pojo index to map from
        res - The DecorationTableParsingResult parsing result (modified by process)
        Returns:
        The model mapped Variable

      • mapUpdates

        private static void mapUpdates​(DecorationTableParsingResult res,
                               TablePOJO tabItem,
                               Instruction inst,
                               java.lang.String semanticLetterLab)
        Maps given update pojo element to model Update and adds it to DecorationTableParsingResult given object. Errors are added to DecorationTableParsingResult.
        Parameters:
        res - The DecorationTableParsingResult parsing result (modified by process)
        tabItem - The table pojo corresponding to this instruction to parse
        inst - The model Instruction where the update value should be added
        semanticLetterLab - The semantic letter corresponding to this instruction
